            Will <m>proj_\vu \vv</m> be parallel to <m>\vu</m> or <m>\vv</m>? Use this answer to explain how you know that the result of <m>proj_\vu \vv</m> must be different than <m>proj_\vv \vu</m> (which we calculated in <xref ref="vecprojex" />).
